until now.

23:01.714 --> 23:04.342
Come on, let's go back.

23:09.346 --> 23:13.396
So that's flight 206
at 1600 hours.

23:13.559 --> 23:16.108
Um, that's 4:00 PM, right?

23:16.270 --> 23:18.819
Okay. No, that's fine.
Thank you.

23:18.981 --> 23:21.575
- Thank you, bye.

23:21.734 --> 23:23.077
