24:10.032 --> 24:14.128
go to see the waterfalls
or to see the caves.

24:14.286 --> 24:16.630
- They are beautiful.
- That sounds like fun.

24:18.249 --> 24:20.297
Ellie.

24:20.459 --> 24:23.554
All right, well, thank you.
Thank you. That's great.

24:42.273 --> 24:44.275
Rosa.

24:46.443 --> 24:48.787
- Permiso, chicas.
- Thanks.

24:53.617 --> 24:55.164
- Come on.
- Huh-uh.

24:55.327 --> 24:57.955
- Come on, Ellie, let's go.
- Huh-uh, no!

24:58.122 --> 24:59.465
Wake up.

24:59.623 --> 25:02.422
Dude, stop!

25:26.400 --> 25:28.698
Oh, look at that.

26:23.791 --> 26:26.010
Wow.

26:29.255 --> 26:31.303
Hey, let's just lay out here.

26:31.465 --> 26:34.218
- Ellie, really?
- Come on, just relax.

26:34.385 --> 26:36.513
We really don't have
anywhere to be.

26:39.682 --> 26:40.934
You win.

27:02.496 --> 27:04.089
Here, sunshine.

27:04.248 --> 27:05.966
It will all be okay.

27:06.125 --> 27:08.219
I promise.

27:12.339 --> 27:14.262
Thanks, El.

27:15.592 --> 27:17.310
- All right.

27:31.108 --> 27:33.907
# I'm feeling blind #

27:34.069 --> 27:36.663
# Like the sun's in my eyes #

27:36.822 --> 27:39.200
# Since I'm fighting in a losing war #

27:39.366 --> 27:43.917
# Tiny little fault lines
cracking inside my soul... #

27:51.962 --> 27:55.262
