28:14.568 --> 28:16.741
I don't know, Steph.
When I'm ready.

28:19.490 --> 28:22.460
Ow! What the hell?
I said I'm not ready.

28:22.618 --> 28:25.713
Well, I am.
El, we can’t be here all day.

28:25.871 --> 28:29.626
You really really need to learn
to have some fun.

28:29.792 --> 28:32.511
And what,
you're gonna teach me, I suppose?

28:32.669 --> 28:35.673
